                <div class="mac_font11px" id="ctl00_cphMainContent_ctl01_divBriefDesc"><div>A harrowing, edge-of-your-seat narrative of murder and secrets, revenge and heroism in the City of Angels, GANGSTER SQUAD chronicles the true story of the secretive police unit that waged an anything-goes war to drive Mickey Cohen and other hoodlums from Los Angeles after WWII.</div></div>
