The Seven Pearls of Financial Wisdom for Women: A talk for every woman who wants to build, preserve and enjoy her wealth. In this speech, the creators of The Seven Pearls philosophy, Carol Pepper and Camilla Webster, offer women guidance in an era of uncharted opportunities and new financial choices. As women's earnings, freedom and influence increase, the old sequential patterns of education, marriage, motherhood, and retirement no longer apply.

Carol and Camilla explain how women now cycle repeatedly- but not in any traditional order through these stages: wealth building, romance and marriage, motherhood, power, crisis and loss, retirement and legacy building. After this talk you will carry away one invaluable pearl of wisdom for each of these key areas. Learn how you can move beyond outdated financial-planning ideas to enjoy your power, transforming both your money and your life.

